Interface NumericalParametrized<T extends NumericalParametrized<T>>

Type Parameters:

All Superinterfaces:
Parametrized<T,double[]>
public interface NumericalParametrized<T extends NumericalParametrized<T>> extends Parametrized<T,double[]>
An object which has a modifiable parameter of type double[], i.e., parametrized with numerical parameters.

  • Method Details

    • randomize

      default void randomize(RandomGenerator randomGenerator, DoubleRange range)
      Randomizes the numerical parameters of this object. Changes each numerical parameter, i.e., element of the double[] parameter of this object, to a new value chosen with uniform probability in range.
      Parameters:
      randomGenerator - the random generator
      range - the interval from which to sample new parameter values with uniform probability
